Detailed Description

cvmx_bgx::_spu::_an_bp_status

The contents of this register are updated during autonegotiation and are valid when BGX()_SPU()_AN_STATUS[AN_COMPLETE] is set. At that time, one of the port type bits ([N100G_CR10], [N40G_CR4], [N40G_KR4], [N10G_KR], [N10G_KX4], [N1G_KX]) will be set depending on the AN priority resolution. If a BASE-R type is negotiated, then [FEC] will be set to indicate that FEC operation has been negotiated, and will be clear otherwise.
